libfreedb-ruby (0.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * length attribute added
  * tracks_ext attribute added (see README)
  * fixed a bug in discid computation
    (Thanks to Akinori MUSHA <knu@iDaemons.org>)
  * protocol level handling
  * code refactoring
