libfreedb-ruby (0.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial Release.
  * fetch() replaced by fetch_net() however i created an alias to fetch()
  * fetch_cgi() added
  * discid read-only attribute added
  * get_cdrom() buffer overrun fixed 

